desc_short	-----								Join the battle for the legendary soul crystals in the fast-paced PvP action game where Class Change is King - BattleSouls! Freely switch between a loadout of three heroes while you are alive, each with his or her own unique abilities, and battle it out in action-packed melee and ranged combat.							
